Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeEmail": "hrmtest@company.com",
  "password": "password123!"
}


### 사원 부서 배치 (HRM 권한 필요)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/organization/employee/department
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "employeeCode": "EMP2604002",
  "departmentId": 1774590557453239
}

### 사원 삭제 (Soft Delete - 상태 변경)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/organization/employee/EMP2603001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 선택 사원 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/organization/employees/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}